title: Interest Rate Paid on Excess Reserve Balances (Institutions with 2-Week Maintenance Period) (DISCONTINUED)
notes: This series has been discontinued due to changes in Regulation D. Effective with the common two-week maintenance period starting on June 27, 2013, balances maintained that exceed the top of the penalty-free band will be remunerated at the interest rate to be paid on excess balances. The new series is at https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/INTRESEXCW?rid=19
